                    "stepText": "After identifying the relationships, use the momentum conservation and the restitution relations to solve for the astronaut's final velocity ($!$v_a$!$). Substitute the known values and isolate $!$v_a$!$. What is the value of $!$v_a$!$?",
                    "stepText2": "",
